The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Robert Kratchel, Appellant.

Order entered on January 31, 1967 unanimously affirmed. No opinion. The order of this court entered on February 20, 1968 [29 A D 2d 846] is vacated. Concur — Steuer, J. P., Capozzoli, McGivern, McNally and Bastow, JJ.
